                                                Is this the year for Cards rookie?

                                    </h4>

        (function() {
            var chance = Math.floor(Math.random() * 100) + 1;
            var percent = +'0' || 0;
            var shouldSwap = chance <= percent;
        
            if (shouldSwap) {
                var elServerMetaTag = document.querySelectorAll('meta[name="server_url"]')[0] || {};
                var serverDomain = elServerMetaTag.content || '';
                var ids = ''
                    .replace(/\s+/g,'')
                    .split(',')
                    .map(function (id) {
                        return 'a.p-headline-stack__link[data-content-id="' + id + '"]';
                    });
        
                var linksSelector = ids.join(',');
        
                document.querySelectorAll(linksSelector).forEach(function (el) {
                    var pathname = el.pathname.replace(/^\//, '');
        
                    el.setAttribute('href', serverDomain + '/' + pathname);
                });
            }
        }());
        </script>

                var width  = window.innerWidth || document.documentElement.clientWidth;
                var height = window.innerHeight || document.documentElement.clientHeight;
                var orientation = (height >= width) ? 'Portrait' : 'Landscape';
                return orientation;
            };

                return str.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + str.substr(1);
            };

        <script type="text/javascript">
            (function(window) {
                'use strict';
        
                // Hack to clear the props not being cleared in s.clearVars().
                var CLEAR_VARS = [
                    'eVar13', 'prop25', 'eVar28', 'prop26', 'prop27',
                    'prop28', 'prop29', 'prop30', 'prop32', 'prop33',
                    'prop34', 'prop43', 'prop49', 'eVar49', 'prop54'
                ];
        
                var clearVars = function(s) {
                    for ( var prop in CLEAR_VARS ) {
                        delete s[ CLEAR_VARS[prop] ];
                    }
        
                    delete s['events'];
                }
        
                var getOrientation = function() {
                    var width  = window.innerWidth || document.documentElement.clientWidth;
                    var height = window.innerHeight || document.documentElement.clientHeight;
                    var orientation = (height >= width) ? 'Portrait' : 'Landscape';
                    return orientation;
                };
        
                var capitalize = function(str) {
                    return str.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + str.substr(1);
                };

                    }

                    s.tl(true, 'o', 'http://myGenericURL');
                };
        
            })(window);

        <script type="text/javascript">
        
            (function() {
        
                var siteJS = {"desktop":"site-desktop","tablet":"site-tablet","phone":"site-phone"};
                var sectionJS = {"desktop":"","tablet":"","phone":""};
                var pageJS = {"desktop":"","tablet":"","phone":""};
                var patternJS = {"alert":true,"scoreboard":true,"ad":true,"mediawall-panel":true,"video-tray":true,"mixed-feed":true,"standings":true,"player-leaderboard":true};
                var type = getStartupDeviceTypeString();
        
        
                /* site and section build=true */
        
                    var siteScripts = [];
                    var scripts = [];
        
                    if (siteJS[type]) {
                        siteScripts.push('//www.mlbstatic.com/mlb.com/builds/site-core/493f1d97b35e2d1c1a3481dc518a38b99f89cae3_1552944113/scripts/'+siteJS[type]+'.js');
                    }
        
                    if (sectionJS[type]) {
                        scripts.push('//www.mlbstatic.com/mlb.com/sections/_pagebuilder/builds/f9250aebf9a92122364b6193ca90f62adad94436_1551198025/scripts/'+sectionJS[type]+'.js');
                    }
        
                    if (pageJS[type]) {
                        scripts.push('//www.mlbstatic.com/mlb.com/sections/_pagebuilder/builds/f9250aebf9a92122364b6193ca90f62adad94436_1551198025/scripts/'+pageJS[type]+'.js');
                    }
        
                    var loadPatternScripts = function () {
                        var patternNames = Object.keys(patternJS);
        
                        if (patternNames.length) {
                            var patternScripts = [];
        
                            patternNames.forEach(function (patternName) {
                                var patternScript = '//www.mlbstatic.com/mlb.com/builds/site-core/493f1d97b35e2d1c1a3481dc518a38b99f89cae3_1552944113/patterns/' + patternName + '/' + patternName + '.js';
                                patternScripts.push(patternScript);
                            });
        
                            requirejs.config({
                                baseUrl: '//www.mlbstatic.com/mlb.com/builds/site-core/493f1d97b35e2d1c1a3481dc518a38b99f89cae3_1552944113/bower_components',
                                waitSeconds: 18,
                                config: {
                                    text: {
                                        useXhr: function (url, protocol, hostname, port) {
                                            return true;
                                        }
                                    }
                                }
                            });
        
                            requirejs(patternScripts);
                        }
                    }
        
                    if (siteScripts.length) {
                        requirejs.config({
                            waitSeconds: 18,
                            paths : {
                                "bam-video-bootstrap": "//www.mlbstatic.com/mlb.com/video/videocore/video"
                            }
                        });
        
                        requirejs(siteScripts, function(){
                            if (scripts.length) {
                                requirejs(scripts, loadPatternScripts);
                            } else {
                                loadPatternScripts();
                            }
                        });
                    }
        
        
            })();
        </script>
